{
  "uid": "v12-admin-prepost",
  "title": "Grafana 12 Admin \u2014 Pre / Post Upgrade Comparison (plugins + dashboards)",
  "description": "Side-by-side inventory of the 11.6.4 instance vs the live 12.4.3 instance. The 'pre' side is a baseline snapshot embedded inline (edit the pre-panel JSON to swap in your own audit output). The 'post' side live-queries /api/plugins and /api/search. Bottom panels compute additions and removals.",
  "tags": [
    "grafana-12",
    "admin",
    "pre-post",
    "comparison",
    "migration",
    "v12-demo"
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 40,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "1m",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-15m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {},
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "ds_api",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource",
        "refresh": 1,
        "current": {
          "text": "Grafana API (Infinity)",
          "value": "grafana-api"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### What this dashboard does\n\n- **Left column = 11.6.4 baseline** \u2014 inline JSON, representing a typical pre-upgrade instance. Replace it with your real audit output (`out/audit-*/plugin_inventory.summary.json` and `out/audit-*/dashboard_inventory.summary.json`) by pasting into the *Query \u2192 Data \u2192 Inline data* field of any baseline panel.\n- **Right column = 12.4.3 live** \u2014 queries the running instance through the Infinity DS.\n- **Diff panels** (bottom) compute *removed* (in baseline, not in live \u2014 usually Angular plugins the migration purged) and *added* (new in 12.4.3 \u2014 usually Drilldown apps + replacements).\n\nAll counts are live. Refresh to re-query."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "PLUGINS \u2014 pre vs post",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 6
      }
    },
